### remaps capslock to esc via udev for the keyboard below
### -- cf. https://github.com/chrisv/udev-key-remap
###
### Input device name: "ROYUAN Akko Multi-modes Keyboard-B"
### Input device ID: bus 0x3 vendor 0x3151 product 0x4003 version 0x111
###
### Manufacturer: Akko/shenzen (China)
### Model: Akko 5087B Plus (TKL-87)
###
evdev:input:b0003v3151p4003*
  KEYBOARD_KEY_70039=esc   # capslock -> esc 
